Wani shark ya kashe wani yaro mai shekara 13 a California yana neman 'yan wasa
Wani shark ya kai hari kuma ya raunana wani yaro mai shekara 13 a ranar Asabar yayin da yake yin ruwa don neman lobsters a California a ranar farko ta kakar lobster, a cewar hukumomi.
An kai harin ne kafin karfe 7 na safe kusa da Beacon's Beach a Encinitas.
Kamar yadda Chad Hammel ya bayyana a San Diego KSWB-TV, ya yi rabin sa'a yana ta yawo tare da wasu abokai a safiyar Asabar lokacin da ya ji kukan wani yaro yana neman taimako.
Hammel ya ce da farko ya yi tunanin cewa farin cikinsa ne ya kama wani gizo-gizo, amma sai ya gane cewa yana ihu 'Sun cije ni!
Sun cije ni!'
Ya yi dukan ƙwayar ƙashin ƙugu, kamar yadda Hammel ya lura lokacin da ya zo wurin yaron.
'Sa'ad da kowa ya fito daga cikin ruwa, sai na yi ihu, 'Akwai wani shark a cikin ruwa!',' in ji Hammel.
An kai yaron ta iska zuwa asibitin Rady Children's Hospital na San Diego, inda aka shigar da shi cikin mummunan yanayi.
Ba a san irin shark da ya kai wannan hari ba.
A wani taron manema labarai, mai aikin agaji Larry Giles ya yi sharhi cewa a cikin 'yan makonni an gano wani shark a yankin, amma an yanke shawarar cewa wannan jinsin ba shi da haɗari.
Giles ya kara da cewa wanda aka kashe ya ji rauni a yankin sama na ƙafarsa.
Hukumomi sun rufe wuraren rairayin bakin teku na tsawon sa'o'i 48 daga Ponto Beach a Casablad zuwa Swami's a Ecinitas saboda bincike da dalilai na tsaro.
Giles ya lura cewa akwai nau'in shark fiye da 135 a yankin, amma yawancin ba su da haɗari.
Sainsbury's yana shirin zuwa kasuwar kayan kwalliyar Burtaniya
Sainsbury's ta yanke shawarar yin gasa a Boots, Superdrug da Debenhams tare da hanyoyin samarda kayayyakin kyau kamar manyan shagunan da ke aiki tare da ma'aikata masu ƙwarewa.
Waɗannan manyan abubuwan da suka faru ne kawai ɓangare na babban saka hannun jari a kasuwar kayan kwalliya a Burtaniya, kasuwar da ke motsawa kusan GBP biliyan 2,8 kuma tana ci gaba da haɓaka yayin da masana'antun kayan ado da kayan gida ke raguwa, kuma za a gwada su a shagunan 11 a duk faɗin ƙasar don faɗaɗa ƙarin shagunan a shekara mai zuwa idan gwajin ya ci nasara.
Saka hannun jari a cikin kayan ado shine samfurin haɗama na manyan kantuna don amfani da sararin samaniya a cikin shagunan da aka yi amfani da su don talabijin, microwaves da kayayyakin gida.
Sainsbury's ta ce za ta ninka tayin ta na kyawawan kayayyaki don samar da samfurori daban-daban har zuwa 3000, gami da a karon farko a cikin alamomi kamar Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman da Dr. PawPaw.
Har ila yau, L'Oreal, Maybelline da Burt's Bees sun sami ƙarin sarari tare da yankunan alama kamar waɗanda za a iya samu a shagunan kamar Boots.
Kamfanin kantin sayar da kayayyaki yana cikin sake ƙaddamar da jerin kayan kwalliyar Boutique don yawancin samfuran yanzu su dace da masu shan giya, wani abu da matasa masu amfani ke neman.
Har ila yau, kantin sayar da kayayyaki na The Fragrance Shop zai bude shaguna a shagunan Sainsbury's guda biyu.
Cinikin intanet da kuma sauya salon cin abinci a kananan kantuna a kowace rana ya sa manyan kantuna su nemi wasu hanyoyin shawo kan mutane su zo.
A cewar Mike Coupe, Shugaba na Sainsbury's, shagunan za su ƙara zama kamar manyan kantuna a cikin ƙoƙarin sarkar manyan kantuna don yaƙi da manyan kantunan Aldi da Lidl tare da ƙarin sabis da samfuran abinci.
Sainsbury's ta gabatar da wuraren sayar da Argos a yawancin manyan kantunan ta, da kuma shaguna da yawa na Habitat tun lokacin da ta sayi duka biyun shekaru biyu da suka gabata, wanda, in ji ta, ya taimaka wajen sake dawo da tallace-tallace na ajiya da haɓaka ribar sayayya.
Ƙoƙarin da aka yi a baya na sarkar sayar da kayayyaki don sake ƙaddamar da sassan kayan ado da kantin magani ya zama rashin nasara.
Sainsbury's ta yi gwajin aiki tare da Boots a farkon shekarun 2000, amma duk abin da ya ƙare da sauri ta hanyar rashin yarda da yadda za a raba fa'idodin sarkar kantin magani a cikin manyan kantuna.
Wannan sabon dabarar ta zo ne bayan Sainsbury's ta sayar da shagonta na shaguna 281 shekaru uku da suka gabata ga Celesio, mai mallakar sarkar LloydsPharmacy, a kan GBP 125 miliyan.
A cewar Sainsbury's, Lloyds zai taka muhimmiyar rawa a cikin shirin duniya, saboda zai faɗaɗa kewayon samfuran samfuran fata masu alatu, kamar La Roche-Posay ko Vichy, zuwa shagunan kasuwanci huɗu.
Paul Mills-Hicks, darektan kasuwanci na Sainsbury's, ya ce: "Mun canja salonmu na kayayyakin ado don mu inganta yanayin da abokan cinikinmu suke ciki.
Mun saka hannun jari a cikin ma'aikata da aka horar da su musamman waɗanda za su taimaka sosai wajen ba da shawara.
An tsara jerin samfuranmu don dacewa da kowane buƙata; a gefe guda, yanayin da ke da kyau da kuma wurin da ake amfani da shi ya sa yanzu muna ɗaya daga cikin wuraren da aka fi so don samfuran kyau kuma muna ƙalubalanci hanyar gargajiya ta siye.
Peter Jones furious bayan Holly Willoughby ya juya baya a kan wani 11 miliyan GBP yarjejeniyar
Tauraron Dragon 'Den Peter Jones ya tafi da sauri bayan mai gabatar da gidan talabijin Holly Willoughby ya yi watsi da yarjejeniyar GBP 11 miliyan tare da kasuwancin Jones na salon rayuwa don mayar da hankali kan sabbin kwangila tare da Marks da Spencer da ITV.
Willoughby ba shi da lokaci don yin kasuwanci tare da kayayyakin gida da kayan haɗi Truly.
Kasuwancin waɗannan haruffan na kafofin watsa labarai biyu sun isa ga kwatancen Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop brand.
Mai gabatar da wannan mujallar Morning mai shekara 37, ta yi amfani da Instagram don sanar da tafiyarta.
Holly Willoughby ya bar tauraron Dragons 'Den Peter Jones cikin fushi ta hanyar janyewa a minti na ƙarshe daga kasuwancin haɗin gwiwa mai fa'ida don mayar da hankali kan sabbin kwangila da kansa tare da Marks & Spencer da ITV, wanda zai kawo masa babbar riba.
A cewar wasu majiyoyi, Jones ya yi fushi lokacin da tauraron talabijin mai launin ja ya yarda, a lokacin wani taro mai rikitarwa da aka gudanar a ranar Talata a hedkwatar mulkinsa a Marlow, Buckinghamshire, cewa sabon yarjejeniyar mai gabatar da, mai darajar GBP miliyan 1,5, ta nuna cewa ba zai ƙara samun isasshen lokacin da zai ba da kansa ga alamar haɗin gwiwar kayayyakin gida da kayan haɗi Truly.
Kasuwancin ya zo da kwatancen Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop brand kuma yana son ninka dukiyar Willoughby, wanda aka kiyasta a GBP 11 miliyan.
Lokacin da Willoughby, mai shekaru 37, ya yi amfani da Instagram don sanar da tafiyarsa daga Truly, Jones ya hau jirgin sama mai zaman kansa zuwa ɗayan wuraren hutun sa a waje da Burtaniya.
A cewar wata majiya: Truly ta kasance babban fifiko na Holly.
Wannan shi ne makomar ta na dogon lokaci kuma za mu gan ta a cikin shekaru 20 zuwa 30.
Shawarwarin da ya yi na janye hankalin dukan waɗanda suka yi hakan ya sa ba a iya magana ba.
Ba wanda zai iya gaskata abin da ya faru a ranar Talata, mun kasance kusa da ƙaddamarwa...
A yanzu haka akwai wani shagon da ke cike da kayayyaki a cibiyarsa a Marlow a shirye don a sayar da su.
Masana sun ce tafiyar mai gabatar da gidan rediyon This Morning, ɗaya daga cikin taurari masu cinikin kuɗi a Burtaniya, na iya kashe kamfanin miliyoyin saboda saka hannun jari mai yawa a cikin kayayyaki, daga matashin kai da fitilu zuwa tufafi da tufafi don gida, da yiwuwar jinkiri don ƙaddamarwa.
Ƙari ga haka, zai iya nufin ƙarshen abokantaka ta dindindin.
Willoughby, mahaifiyar 'ya'ya uku, da mijinta Dan Baldwin sun kasance cikin dangantaka mai kyau da Jones da matarsa Tara Capp na shekaru goma.
Willoughby ya kafa Truly tare da Capp a 2016, kuma Jones, 52, ya shiga ciki yana rike da mukamin shugaban a watan Maris da ya gabata.
Dukansu ma'aurata suna yin hutu tare. Bugu da ƙari, Jones yana da kashi 40 cikin ɗari na hannun jari a cikin kamfanin talabijin na Baldwin.
Willoughby za ta zama jakadan alama na gaba na M&S kuma za ta maye gurbin Ant McPartlin a matsayin mai gabatar da shirin I'm A Celebrity na ITV.
Wata majiya da ke kusa da Jones ta ce a jiya za mu yi sharhi game da kasuwancinsa.
Mun yi mu'amala da juna bayan mun yi zargi mai tsanani.
Ya yi dariya game da yiwuwar sukar da ya samu daga kafofin watsa labarai don yin tsokaci wanda wasu za su ɗauka ba daidai ba ne ga shugaban kasar kuma don samun irin wannan kyakkyawan ra'ayi game da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa.
