Rashin guguwar Rosa zai kawo ruwan sama mai yawa a kudancin yammacin Amurka
A cewar hasashen, Hurricane Rosa yana raunana yayin da yake tafiya a kan ruwan sanyi na arewacin tekun Mexico.
