A ranar Litinin, ruwan sama mai yawa zai sauka a wasu sassan Mexico.
Bayan haka, zafi mai zafi zai yi hulɗa da yanayin da ke gabatowa don haifar da ruwan sama mai yawa a duk kudu maso yammacin cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
