Mutane sama da miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shaidar shaidar da ake yi wa dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh da kuma matar da ta zarge shi da cin zarafin jima'i, wanda ake zargin ya faru a shekarun 1980, Christine Blasey Ford.
A halin yanzu, rashin ci gaba na siyasa ya ci gaba, tare da masu watsa shirye-shirye sun katse jadawalin yau da kullun na Jumma'a saboda juyin juya halin da ya faru a minti na ƙarshe: yarjejeniya da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya tsara don FBI ta gudanar da bincike game da zargin na mako guda.
Ford ta bayyana wa Kwamitin Majalisar Dattijai don Batutuwan Shari'a cewa ta tabbata cewa Kavanaugh ya taɓa ta a lokacin da ta sha giya kuma ta yi ƙoƙarin cire tufafinta a wani biki na makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh, a cikin wani shaida mai girma, ya bayyana cewa ya tabbata cewa wannan bai taɓa faruwa ba.
A cewar Nielsen, mutane fiye da miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli wannan shaidar a ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin yana da matsakaicin masu kallo na tashoshin CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samun lambobin sauraro nan da nan ta sauran tashoshin da suka watsa shaidar ba, kamar PBS, C-SPAN ko Fox Business Network.
Bugu da ƙari, Nielsen yana da matsala wajen ƙayyade yawan mutanen da ke kallon shi daga ofishinsa.
