Fox News Channel, wanda shugabannin ra'ayin jama'a suka ba da cikakken goyon baya ga nadin Kavanaugh, shine tashar da ta fi sauraro, tare da matsakaicin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a lokacin shaidar kwana ɗaya, a cewar Nielsen.
ABC ta biyu ne da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS ta samu miliyan 3,1, NBC miliyan 2,94, MSNBC miliyan 2,89 da CNN miliyan 2,52, a cewar bayanan Nielsen.
