'Yan sanda sun kama wani wanda ake zargi da kisan da aka yi wa Wayde Sims, dan wasan kwando mai shekaru 20 da haihuwa wanda ke aiki a kungiyar LSU.
An kama Dyteon Simpson, mai shekara 20, kuma an tura shi kurkuku bisa zargin kisa na biyu, a cewar sashen 'yan sanda na Baton Rouge.
