Livingston, wanda a wannan shekara ya tashi daga matsayi, ya ba da mamaki ga Glasgow Rangers a cikin abin da ke daidai shine rasa Steven Gerrard na biyu a wasanni 18 a matsayin kocin kulob din Yankin Ibrox.
