Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia, inda adadin mutanen da suka mutu ya ci gaba da ƙaruwa
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu, da yawa daga cikinsu an ja su da igiyar ruwa mai zurfi da ke ragargaza rairayin bakin teku, sakamakon girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani da tsunami da ya shafi tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia, kamar yadda hukumomi suka ce a ranar Asabar.
Daruruwan mutane sun taru a ranar Juma'a don bikin da ake yi a bakin rairayin bakin teku a birnin Palu lokacin da raƙuman ruwa na tsawon mita shida suka yi tasiri a bakin teku a yammacin yamma, suna jan mutane da yawa zuwa mutuwa kuma suna lalata duk abin da suka samu a hanyarsu.
An bi tsunami da girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5.
"Lokacin da ake fuskantar barazanar tsunami a jiya, mutane suna ci gaba da aikinsu a bakin rairayin bakin teku kuma ba su gudu ba, saboda haka sun zama wadanda aka azabtar", in ji Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, kakakin hukumar hana kawo bala'i BNPB a wata sanarwa a Jakarta.
Tsunami bai zo shi kaɗai ba, ya jawo motoci, bishiyoyi, gidaje, ya lalata duk abin da ke ƙasa, in ji Nugroho, yana ƙara da cewa tsunami ya yi tafiya a teku a cikin saurin kilomita 800 a kowace awa kafin ya buga gabar teku.
Ta ce wasu sun hau kan wani itace don su tsira daga tsunami.
An yi garkuwa da mutane 16,700 a cibiyoyi 24 a Palu.
Hotunan da hukumar hana bala'i ta wallafa a sararin sama sun nuna yawan shagunan da gine-gine da aka rushe, da gadoji da aka juya da kuma rufaffiyar ruwa da kuma masallaci da aka kewaye da ruwa.
A ranar Asabar, an ci gaba da yin tawaye a wannan garin.
An ji girgizar ƙasa a wani yanki na mutane miliyan 2.4.
Hukumar tantancewa da kuma amfani da fasahar Indonesia (BPPT) ta ce a wata sanarwa, ƙarfin da girgizar ƙasa ta yi a ranar Juma'a ya yi amfani da shi ya ninka ƙarfin da aka yi amfani da shi a lokacin yakin duniya na biyu.
A cewar hukumar, yanayin yanayin garin, wanda ke ƙarshen dogon bakin teku, na iya ƙara girman tsunami sosai.
Nugroho ya bayyana lalacewar a matsayin "mai mahimmanci" kuma ya ce dubban gidaje, asibitoci, cibiyoyin kasuwanci da otal-otal sun rushe.
An gano gawarwakin wasu daga cikin wadanda aka kashe, in ji ta, a tsakanin ruwan gine-gine da suka rushe, ta ƙara da cewa mutane 540 sun ji rauni kuma 29 sun ɓace.
A cewar Nugroho, mutuwar da lalacewar na iya ƙaruwa a bakin teku a kusan kilomita 300 arewacin Palu, wani yanki da ake kira Donggala, mafi kusa da tsakiyar girgizar ƙasa.
Dukkanin hanyoyin sadarwa sun kasance a kwance kuma ba a samun wani bayani daga Donggala ba, in ji Nugroho.
Ƙungiyar ta Red Cross ta ce mutane fiye da 300,000 ne ke zaune a wurin, kuma ta ce ma'aikatanta da masu aikin sa kai suna zuwa wuraren da ake fama da cutar.
"Wannan masifa ce, kuma abin takaici, za ta iya zama mafi muni", in ji shi.
An soki hukumar sosai a ranar Asabar saboda rashin bayar da rahoton tsunami a Palu, duk da cewa jami'an sun ce raƙuman ruwa sun zo a lokacin da aka ba da sanarwar.
A wani sakon da wani mai son yin fim ya wallafa a shafukan sada zumunta, za a iya jin wani mutum a bene yana ihu yana gargaɗi mutane game da tsunami mai zuwa.
A cikin 'yan mintoci kaɗan, wani ganuwar ruwa ya fashe a bakin teku, yana ɗauke gine-gine da motoci.
Kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters bai iya tabbatar da cewa an yi rikodin ba.
Girgizar kasa da tsunami sun haifar da yanke wutar lantarki wanda ya katse sadarwa a kusa da Palu, yana sa ya zama da wahala ga hukumomi su daidaita ayyukan ceto.
Duk da cewa sojojin sun fara aika agaji ta jirgin sama daga Jakarta da wasu birane, hukumomi sun ce mutanen da aka kwashe suna bukatar abinci da kuma wasu abubuwan da suka fi muhimmanci.
Filin jirgin saman birnin ya sake buɗewa don ayyukan taimako kawai kuma zai kasance a rufe har zuwa Oktoba.
Shugaban kasar Joko Widodo ya shirya ziyartar cibiyoyin kwashe mutane a Palu a ranar Lahadi.
Yawan mutanen da suka mutu a sakamakon tsunami a Indonesia ya kai 800.
Yanayin yana da tsanani.
Duk da cewa ma'aikatan kamfanin World Vision a Donggala sun isa birnin Palu lafiya da lafiya, inda ma'aikatan ke aiki a cikin wuraren ajiye kayan ado da aka sanya a cikin farfajiyar ofishinsu, a lokacin tafiya sun fuskanci abubuwan da suka faru na lalata, in ji Doseba.
Sun ce sun ga gidaje da yawa sun lalace, in ji shi.
