Taron Trump a West Virginia, Tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara wani taron yakin neman zabe a daren yau a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan ne na farko daga cikin tarurrukan Trump guda biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da ziyara a wurare masu kyau, kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da aka yi wa Trump rajistar amincewa da shi a matsayin dan takararsa na babban kotun, Trump yana neman samun goyon baya a zaben rabin lokaci na gaba, saboda 'yan Republican suna fuskantar haɗarin rasa ikon Majalisar Dokoki lokacin da aka jefa kuri'u a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump zai kasance a West Virginia a daren yau, kuma yaya za a iya duba shi a layi?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, an shirya shi ne a karfe 19 na yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Ana iya ganin taron Trump a West Virginia ta yanar gizo a hanyar haɗin da aka ƙayyade a ƙasa, ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen bidiyo kai tsaye ta YouTube.
Ana iya ganin Trump zai yi magana game da sauraron da aka fara a wannan makon tare da dan takarar da aka nada a Kotun Koli, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya kasance mai rikitarwa saboda zargin cin zarafin jima'i da yake fuskanta, yayin da aka shirya Majalisar Dattawa don amincewa da shi har zuwa mako guda kuma FBI tana binciken lamarin.
Amma babban burin wannan taron taron shine taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke neman shiga cikin zaɓe mai mahimmanci na Nuwamba don samun ci gaba.
Saboda haka, taron biyar na yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, ana nufin su karfafa masu sa kai da masu goyon baya, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjayen da suke da su a Majalisar Dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai, in ji Reuters.
"Sarrafawa a majalisar dokoki yana da mahimmanci ga tsarinsa cewa shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da yawa kamar yadda zai iya, yayin da muke tafiya zuwa wani lokacin yakin neman zabe mai cike da damuwa", in ji wani mai magana da yawun Trump wanda ya ki bayyana sunan sa, a cewar Reuters.
Taron da aka shirya a Wesbanco Arena, Wheeling, zai iya tara masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, kuma ya jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne karo na biyu da Trump ya ziyarci West Virginia, jihar da ya ci nasara da maki sama da 40 a cikin 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa Patrick Morrisey, dan takarar Republican a majalisar dattijai ta West Virginia, wanda ke samun sakamako mara kyau a cikin binciken.
"Ba wata alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo ya ba shi damar gudanar da bincike", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
