Wannan mata da miji na Turai suna da 'yan hudu daga cikin hudu kuma ba su yin kuskure ba.
Moliwood sun kasance ma'aurata kawai da ba su yi bogey a ranar Asabar da yamma ba, kuma sun kuma guji bogey a ranar Asabar da safe da Jumma'a da yamma, da kuma karshe tara a ranar Jumma'a da safe.
Saboda wannan sakamakon da kuma yadda makamashi yake gudana zuwa da kuma daga cikin masu sauraro masu ban tsoro, an sake tabbatar da cewa su ne 'yan wasan da za su buga ranar Lahadi, kuma babu wani ɗan wasa da ya fi shahara fiye da Fleetwood ko Molinari don rufe yiwuwar nasarar Turai yayin da rana ta faɗi a kan Le Golf National.
Zai fi kyau su yi aiki a lokaci guda a cikin ramuka daban-daban.
Amma, yin magana game da ɗaukakar Turai ya yi kama da wuri.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi sauri suka kawo karshen Sergio Garcia, gwarzon wasan safiya, wanda ya yi aure da Alex Noren.
Wani bogey da biyu biyu a cikin ramuka tara na farko sun jefa Mutanen Espanya da Swede cikin rami wanda ba su taɓa samun damar fita ba.
A ranar Lahadi, babu wanda zai iya taimaka maka ka fita daga rami.
Masu amfani da wayoyi masu yawa suna da ban sha'awa sosai don ganin yadda kayan aiki ke hulɗa, shawarwarin da suke bayarwa da waɗanda ba su bayarwa, da kuma yadda dabarun zai iya canzawa lokaci zuwa lokaci.
A yanzu dai, Turai ta yi aiki mafi kyau a matsayin tawagar kuma za ta fuskanci ranar ƙarshe da babbar fa'ida, amma wannan taron na hudu ya nuna cewa tawagar Amurka tana da dalili don yin gwagwarmaya wanda wasu, musamman Amurka, suka yi tambaya.
Turai ta kai karshe a gasar cin kofin Ryder ta cin nasara da maki 10-6
Turai za ta fuskanci Ryder Cup na karshe a rana ta ƙarshe tare da fa'ida mai kyau bayan kammala wasan motsa jiki da wasan motsa jiki na Asabar tare da nasara ta 10 zuwa 6 a kan Amurka.
Duo mai ban sha'awa wanda ya ƙunshi Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari ya yi ƙoƙari sosai don samun nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods mai wahala kuma ya bar rikodin sa, har zuwa yanzu, a maki huɗu a Le Golf National.
Ƙungiyar Turai, wanda Thomas Bjorn ya jagoranci, wanda ke neman ya riƙe kyautar da ya rasa shekaru biyu da suka gabata a Hazeltine, ya rinjayi ƙungiyar Amurka da ba ta dace ba a cikin wasannin safiya kuma ya sanya jerin a 3-1.
Amurka ta kara tsayayya da 'yan wasan hudu kuma ta lashe wasanni biyu, amma ba ta iya rage bambancin ba.
Ƙungiyar Jim Furyk ta buƙaci samun maki takwas a wasannin 12 na Lahadi don riƙe kyautar.
Fleetwood shine farkon dan wasan Turai da ya fara samun maki huɗu a jere, yayin da shi da Molinari, waɗanda aka sani da sunan mahaifi na Molliwood bayan ƙarshen mako mai ban mamaki, sune kawai ma'aurata na biyu da suka sami maki huɗu a farkon wasanninsu huɗu a tarihin Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun kori Woods da Patrick Reed zuwa cikin 'yan wasan hudu, sun yi kyakkyawan aiki don doke Woods da Amurkawa Bryson Dechambeau da 5&4 mafi ban sha'awa.
Woods, wanda ya yi tsalle a wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna wasu abubuwan da suka faru na lokaci-lokaci, amma ya rasa wasanni 19 daga 29 a cikin fourballs da foursomes, da kuma bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda bai halarci wasan hudu na safe ba, ya sake yin aure tare da Henrik Stenson a wasan hudu kuma ya fadi 2-1 a kan Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka, wanda aka sanya a matsayin na farko da na uku a duniya, bi da bi.
Amma, ba a yi wa Turai nasara ba a ranar da ake da iska mai kyau a kudu maso yammacin birnin Paris.
Jordan Spieth, wanda ya lashe gasar sau uku, da Justin Thomas sun kafa ranar Asabar wani maki na alama ga Amurkawa ta hanyar samun maki biyu.
Sun sami nasara ta 2 ga 1 a kan Mutanen Espanya Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter a cikin fourballs kuma, daga baya, sun sake cin nasarar Poulter da Rory McIlroy ta 4 ga 3 a cikin foursomes, bayan sun rasa ramukan farko biyu.
Sau biyu kawai a tarihin Ryder Cup wani rukuni ya sami bambanci na maki huɗu a wasannin mutum, kodayake ƙungiyar Furyk, mai kare taken, kawai tana buƙatar daidaitawa don kiyaye shi.
Duk da haka, bayan kasancewa na biyu mafi kyau na kwanaki biyu, yana da alama cewa wani counterattack na Lahadi mai zuwa ya fita daga cikin ikon.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za ta yi watsi da makamai ba a kowane hali sai an nuna tabbacin amincewa
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya sanar da Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa ci gaba da takunkumi na kara karfafa rashin amincewarsu da Amurka kuma a irin wannan yanayin, kasar ba za ta kawar da makaman nukiliya ta kowane hali ba.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa Babban Taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki muhimman matakan kirki a shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da na makami mai linzami, rushe cibiyar gwajin makaman nukiliya da kuma yin alkawarin kada ta yada makamai da fasahar nukiliya.
"Amma ba mu ga wani amsa ba a Amurka", in ji shi.
"Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba, ba za a amince da tsaronmu na kasa ba, kuma a irin wannan yanayin ba za mu fara sasantawa ba a kowane hali.
Duk da yake Ri ya sake yin korafin da aka sani na Koriya ta Arewa game da juriya ta Washington ga tsarin hana nukiliya ta mataki  wanda Koriya ta Arewa za ta ba da lada yayin da ta ɗauki matakan mataki-mataki, maganganun ta sun zama masu mahimmanci saboda gaskiyar cewa ba ta ƙi cikakken hana nukiliya ba, kamar yadda Pyongyang ta riga ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi magana ne game da sanarwar da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka yi a taron koli na farko tsakanin shugaban Amurka mai aiki da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga Yuni, inda Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki a kan 'yancin nukiliya na yankin Koriya ta Arewa', yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin tabbacin tsaro ga Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi ƙoƙari ta kawo ƙarshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta sanar da cewa kafin Pyongyang ta kawar da makaman nukiliya.
Washington ta kuma tsayayya da kiran da ake yi na sassauta tsauraran takunkumin da kasashen duniya suka sanya wa Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta nace cewa dole ne a fara da kawar da makaman nukiliya kuma ta kara matsin lamba tare da takunkumi don cimma burinta ta hanyar tilastawa, ban da adawa da "sanarwar kawo karshen yaki", Ri ya nuna.
Hukumar da ke nuna cewa za a yi mu a kan gwiwoyinmu ita ce abin da mutanen da ba su san kome ba game da mu suke yi.
Amma matsalar ita ce, ci gaba da sanya takunkumi yana kara yawan rashin amincewarmu.
Ri bai ambaci shirin da zai yi na biyu na taron koli tsakanin Kim da Trump ba wanda shugaban Amurka ya yi magana a kan shi a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon nan.
Maimakon haka, Ministan ya nuna tarurruka uku da Kim ya yi da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata, kuma ya kara da cewa: Idan da hannu a batun batun hana makaman nukiliya ya kasance Koriya ta Kudu maimakon Amurka, hana makaman nukiliya na yankin Koriya ba zai kai ga wannan halin da ake ciki ba.
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Ri ya bambanta da na bara, lokacin da ya bayyana a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ƙaddamar da Amurka tare da makamai masu linzami na Arewacin Koriya ba makawa ne bayan shugaban kasar Mr. Evil Trump ya kira Kim Rocket Man a cikin aikin kashe kansa.
A Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Trump, wanda a bara ya yi barazanar lalata Koriya ta Arewa gaba daya, ya yaba wa Kim don ƙarfin zuciyarsa na daukar matakan kawar da makamai, amma ya bayyana cewa akwai sauran aiki da yawa da za a yi kuma dole ne a ci gaba da sanya takunkumi har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta kawar da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba da ta gabata, Trump ya ce babu wani lokaci da za a yi hakan kuma ba kome ko shekaru biyu, shekaru uku ko watanni biyar suka wuce.
Kasashen Sin da Rasha sun ce Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta bukaci Pyongyang ta ba da lada saboda matakan da ta dauka.
Duk da haka, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka, Mike Pompeo, ya bayyana a ranar Alhamis a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa: "Tallafin takunkumin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya kamata ya ci gaba da karfi kuma ba tare da wani abu ba har sai mun tabbatar da cikakken kawar da makaman nukiliya.
Majalisar tsaron kasar ta amince da takunkumi a kan Koriya ta Arewa tun shekara ta 2006 a wani mataki na yanke kudaden da ake kashewa kan shirye-shiryen makaman nukiliya da makaman kwarya na Pyongyang.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a wajen babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sannan ya sanar da cewa zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron koli na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekara, amma ba ya tafiya sosai a wannan shekarar.
Ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana cewa an samu ci gaba, amma bayan 'yan sa'o'i kaɗan Koriya ta Arewa ta zarge shi da yin 'bukatun' 'yan bindigan.
A wani taron da ta yi da Moon a wannan watan, Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin rushe wani cibiyar harbe-harbe da kuma makaman nukiliya idan Amurka ta ɗauki matakan da suka dace.
Ya ce Kim ya sanar da shi cewa matakan tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawari a Singapore ne, ban da matakan daidaita dangantakar da Washington.
Daliban Harvard suna koyar da wani darasi game da yawan hutu
A shekarar da ta gabata, wani sabon darasi a Jami'ar Harvard ya sa dalibansa su yi barci sosai, a wani yunkuri na yaki da al'adun da ake ci gaba da fadada su na nazarin dare, wanda ake amfani da shi wajen karfafa maganin kafeyin.
Wani masanin kimiyya ya lura cewa ɗaliban jami'a na farko a duniya suna yawan damuwa game da muhimman abubuwan da suka shafi yadda za su kula da kansu.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa a likitancin barci a Harvard Medical School kuma gwani a asibitin Brigham da Mata, ya tsara wannan darasin, wanda ya yi imanin cewa shi ne na farko a Amurka.
Ya yi wahayi zuwa ga ƙirƙirar darasin bayan ya yi magana game da tasirin rashin barci a ilmantarwa.
A ƙarshen wannan tattaunawar, wata yarinya ta zo wurina ta ce, 'Me ya sa ake gaya mini dukan waɗannan abubuwa yanzu, tun ina ƙarami?'
Ta ce ba a taɓa gaya mata muhimmancin barci ba, kuma hakan ya ba ni mamaki, in ji ta a jaridar The Telegraph.
A cikin wannan darasin, wanda aka fara aiwatarwa a wannan shekara, an bayyana wa ɗalibai mahimman ra'ayoyi game da yadda kyawawan halaye na barci ke inganta ƙwarewar ilimi da wasanni, ban da lafiyar gaba ɗaya.
Paul Barreira, Farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar dan adam a Harvard Medical School kuma babban darektan kula da lafiyar jami'ar, ya bayyana cewa Jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da karatun bayan ta fahimci cewa wasu ɗalibai suna fama da rashin bacci mai tsanani a cikin mako.
Wannan darasi na tsawon sa'a guda ya ƙunshi ayyuka masu ma'amala.
A wani sashe akwai hoton ɗakin kwana, inda ɗalibai ke danna kofuna na kofi, labule, da littattafai don samun bayani game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske, yadda wasanni ke shafar rashin barci, da kuma muhimmancin yin aiki na yau da kullum don barci.
A wani sashe kuma, an yi wa masu halartar taron bayani game da yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya ƙara haɗarin ciwon zuciya, ɓarkewar kwakwalwa, baƙin ciki, da kuma ciwon daji.
Bayan haka, taswirar harabar da aka yi amfani da ita ta nuna alamomin da za su iya taimaka wa ɗalibai su yi tunani game da hanyarsu ta yau da kullum.
Mun san cewa halin ɗalibai ba zai canja nan take ba.
Amma mun yi imani cewa suna da hakkin su san hakan, kamar yadda mutum yake da hakkin sanin sakamakon shan sigari ga lafiyarsa, in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Ya ce har ila yau, al'adar alfahari da kasancewa a farke a daren jiya tana nan, kuma ya kara da cewa fasahar zamani da kuma matsin lamba da ake yi wa ɗalibai ya sa rashin barci ya zama matsala mai tsanani.
Tabbatar da samun isasshen bacci na dogon lokaci ya kamata ya zama makami na sirri ga dalibai don magance damuwa, gajiya da damuwa, in ji shi, har ma don kauce wa samun nauyi, saboda rashin barci yana sa kwakwalwa ta yi barci kuma yana sa ɗalibai su ci abinci kullum.
Raymond So, ɗan shekara 19 a California wanda ke nazarin Kimiyya da Kimiyya ta Fasaha, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler wajen tsara darasin, bayan ya halarci ɗayan azuzuwansa a shekarar ƙarshe a lokacin shekararsa ta farko a Harvard.
Raymond ya ce wannan darasin ya buɗe masa idanu kuma ya sa ya yi wa darasin wahayi zuwa ga dukan harabar.
Ya ce mataki na gaba shi ne a nemi ɗaliban digiri na biyu su yi irin wannan shirin kafin su shiga makarantar gasa.
Farfesa Czeisler ya shawarci ɗalibai su yi la'akari da sanya ƙararrawa a lokacin barci da farkawa, kuma su san tasirin cutarwa na haske mai launin shuɗi da allon lantarki da hasken LED ke fitarwa, wanda zai iya lalata jituwa na bugun jini da haifar da matsalolin barci.
