Almanac: mai kirkiro na lissafin Geiger
Yanzu kuma shafi na "Sunday Morning" Almanac: 30 ga Satumba, 1882, shekaru 136 da suka gabata, kuma yana ƙidaya... ranar da aka haifi masanin kimiyyar lissafi na nan gaba, Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger, a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanya don ganowa da auna aikin rediyo, wani abu da ya haifar da na'urar da muka sani da computer Geiger.
Geiger Counter, wanda ya kasance ginshiƙi na kimiyya tun daga wannan lokacin, ya kuma zama tarin al'adun gargajiya, kamar fim din 1950 "Bells of Coronado", wanda Roy Rogers da Dale Evans suka taka leda, masu ilimin lissafi na Cowboys da suka gaza:
Mutum: "Wane irin hakori ne wannan?"
Rogers: "Wannan shi ne mai lissafin Geiger, wanda ake amfani da shi wajen gano ma'adinai masu radiyo kamar uranium.
Idan ka saka waɗannan belun kunne, za ka iya jin yadda kwayoyin da ke fitowa daga rediyo suke shafan ma'adinai".
Evans: "Lalle ne yana fashewa yanzu!"
"Hans" Geiger ya mutu a 1945, kwanaki kadan bayan ranar haihuwarsa ta 63.
Amma abin da ya sa aka kira shi da sunansa yana da rai.
Wani sabon allurar rigakafin cutar kansa zai iya koya wa tsarin garkuwar mutum ya kashe ƙwayoyin cutar
Sabuwar allurar rigakafin cutar kansa na iya koya wa tsarin garkuwar mutum ya rayu kuma ya kawar da ƙwayoyin cutar
Allurar rigakafi tana koya wa tsarin garkuwar mutum gane ƙwayoyin cuta a matsayin wani ɓangare na magani
Wannan hanya tana nufin cire kwayoyin rigakafi daga cikin marasa lafiya kuma a canja su a dakin gwaje-gwaje
Za ka iya ganin furotin da yake da yawa a cikin cututtukan daji, sannan ka sake yin amfani da shi
Wani gwajin da ake yi na allurar rigakafi yana nuna sakamako mai kyau ga marasa lafiya da ke fama da nau'o'in ciwon daji daban-daban.
Wata mata da aka yi wa allurar rigakafi, wadda ta koya wa tsarin garkuwar jiki yadda za ta gane ƙwayoyin cuta, ta ga ciwon daji na ovarian ya ƙare tun bayan ta yi watanni 18.
Hanyar ta ƙunshi cire ƙwayoyin rigakafi daga cikin marasa lafiya, canja su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje don "duba" furotin da ke cikin nau'ikan ciwon daji da yawa (HER2) kuma, daga baya, sake yin allura.
Farfesa Jay Berzofsky na Cibiyar Kula da Ciwon daji ta Amirka, a Bethesda, Maryland, ya ce: "Binciken da muka samu ya nuna cewa muna da alurar riga kafi mai kyau".
Fitowar HER2 tana taimaka wa ciwon daji na wasu nau'o'in daji, ciki har da na nono, na ovaries, na huhu da na colorectal, in ji Farfesa Berzofsky.
Irin wannan tsarin da ake bi wajen cire ƙwayoyin rigakafi daga marasa lafiya da kuma koya musu yadda za su bi da ƙwayoyin daji ya yi tasiri wajen magance wani nau'in cutar sankarar jini.
