Kanye West ya shiga cikin ɗakin karatu a lokacin shirin Saturday Night Live bayan wani wasan kwaikwayo mai ban tsoro inda ya taya Shugaban Amurka, Donald Trump murna, kuma ya ce zai tsaya takara a zaben 2020.
Bayan waƙar ta uku ta dare, mai taken Ghost Town, wanda ya sa takalmin Make America Great Again, ya fara sukar 'yan Democrat da kuma sake tabbatar da goyon bayansa ga Trump.
"Duk lokacin da na yi magana da fararen fata, suna cewa, 'Yaya za ka so Trump idan shi ɗan wariyar launin fata ne?
Idan na damu da wariyar launin fata, da na bar Amurka tun da daɗewa", in ji ta.
Shirin SNL ya fara da satirical Matt Damon, inda Hollywood star ya yi ba'a da shaidar Brett Kavanaugh a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattijai don zargin cin zarafin jima'i da Christine Blasey Ford ta gabatar.
Ko da yake ba a watsa shi ba, ɗan wasan kwaikwayo Chris Rock ya ɗaga rikodin rashin amincewa da West a kan kafofin watsa labarun.
Ba a bayyana ko Rock yana so ya yi wa West ba'a tare da buga shi ba.
Duk da haka, West ya yi korafi ga jama'a cewa ba a yi masa kyau a cikin gidajen ba saboda hatinsa.
"An yi mini barazana a cikin gidajen da aka kafa.
Sun gaya mini kada ka fita da wannan hular a rufe.
Sun kama ni.
Sai suka ce ina cikin wani matsayi na kasa", in ji shi, a cewar Washington Examiner.
West ya ci gaba da cewa, "Kuna son ganin matsayin da ke ƙasa?" yayin da yake cewa zai sa Superman ya sa tufafinsa domin ba za su iya gaya masa abin da ya yi ba. "Kuna son duniya ta ci gaba?
Ka yi ƙoƙari ka ƙi".
Maganarsa ta haifar da ra'ayoyin jama'a aƙalla sau biyu kuma membobin ƙungiyar shirin sun zama kamar sun ji kunya, a cewar Variety, wanda ya yi wani mai ba da rahoto wanda ya bayyana wa littafin: "Dukan binciken ya zama a banza".
West ya ɗauki matsayin maye gurbin Aryana Grande, wanda tsohon rapper Mac Miller ya mutu 'yan kwanaki da suka gabata.
West ya ba da mamaki ga yawancin masu sauraro tare da yin waƙar I Love it, sanye da kwalban Perrier.
West ya sami goyon bayan shugaban kungiyar TPUSA, Candace Turner, wanda ya yi rubutu a shafinsa na Twitter: "Ga daya daga cikin masu karfin zuciya: Godiya don fita cikin mutane".
Amma mai gabatar da shirin, Karen Hunter, ta wallafa cewa West "yana da shi ne kawai kuma yana da ban mamaki".
"Amma na zaɓi kada in ba da lada ga wani (ta hanyar sayen kiɗa ko tufafi ko kuma ta hanyar tallafawa 'fasaha') wanda na yi imani ya ɗauki kuma ya yada wani ra'ayi da ke cutar da al'ummarmu.
Yana da free.
Mu ma muna da irin wannan halin", in ji shi.
Kafin wasan, rapper ya sanar a Twitter cewa sunansa ya canza kuma yanzu "wanda aka fi sani da Kanye West".
Ba shi ne mai fasaha na farko da ya canza sunan ba kuma ya bi sawun Diddy, wanda aka fi sani da Puff Daddy, Puffy da P Diddy.
Abokin aikinsa mai suna Snoop Dogg, a baya ake kira Snoop Lion kuma an canza sunan Prince zuwa alama kuma daga baya, mai zane wanda aka sani da Prince.
