'Yan sanda sun ce an yi wannan hatsarin ne a garin Ballyhackamore.
Ana sa ran wanda ake tuhuma zai bayyana a gaban kotun farko a Belfast a ranar Litinin.
Sakataren zai duba zargin.
Tauraron Wasannin Dauki, Kit Harington, Ta Bayyana Mutumin Da Ke Da Guba
Kit Harington ya shahara sosai don yin rawar da ake kira Jon Snow a cikin jerin wasan kwaikwayo na HBO Game da kursiyai.
Duk da haka, dan wasan mai shekaru 31, ya yi tir da stereotype na jarumi, yana mai cewa waɗannan ayyukan suna nuna cewa matasa matasa sukan gaskata cewa dole ne su kasance masu ƙarfi don a girmama su.
A wata hira da jaridar The Sunday Times ta Culture, Kit ya ce yana ganin wani abu ya tafi daidai ba kuma yana tambayar yadda za a magance matsalar namiji mai guba a bayan #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri co-star na Game da kursiyai, Rose Leslie, mai shekaru 31, ya yarda cewa yana da ƙuduri sosai don magance wannan matsalar.
"Na yi mamakin inda muka yi kuskure game da namiji", in ji ta.
Mene ne muka koya wa mutane a lokacin da suka ci gaba da ci gaba game da matsalar da muke fuskanta a yanzu?
A cewar Kit, talabijin na iya ɗaukar nauyin ƙara yawan namiji mai guba saboda halayensa masu ƙarfi.
Ya kara da cewa: "Mecece haihuwar, kuma mece ce ake samu?
Mene ne ake nufi da talabijin da kuma talabijin da ke sa matasa maza su ji cewa suna bukatar su kasance da irin wannan halin?
Ina ganin wannan na daga cikin manyan tambayoyin zamaninmu: ta yaya za mu canza shi?
Domin babu shakka an yi wani abu ba daidai ba da matasa boys.
A cikin hira, ya kuma yarda cewa ba zai yi wani prequel ko sequel na Game da kursiyai lokacin da ƙarshen jerin ya shirya don bazara mai zuwa ba, duk yana cewa ya gaji da yaƙe-yaƙe da dawakai.
Daga watan Nuwamba, Kit zai taka rawa a cikin sake buga aikin Sam Shepard na True West, wanda ke ba da labarin wani mai samar da fim da ɗan'uwansa, wanda ɓarawo ne.
A kwanan nan, actor ya bayyana cewa sanin abokin aikinsa Rose shine mafi kyawun abin da ya ba shi Game da kursiyai.
"Na sadu da matata a cikin wasan kwaikwayon, don haka ta ba ni iyalina na gaba da rayuwata a gaba", in ji ta.
Rose ta yi rawar Ygritte, ƙaunar halin da Kit ke wakilta, Jon Snow, a cikin jerin abubuwan da suka lashe Emmy.
Ma'auratan sun yi aure a watan Yuni na 2018 a gonar Leslie, a Scotland.
HIV/AIDS: China ta ba da rahoton karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na sababbin kamuwa da cutar
Kasar Sin ta ba da sanarwar karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS.
Jami'an lafiya sun ce mutane fiye da 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a kasar.
A cikin kashi na biyu na shekara ta 2018 kawai, an samu sabbin mutane 40,000.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka na jima'i ne, ba kamar yadda suke a dā ba.
A wasu yankunan ƙasar Sin, HIV yana yaduwa da sauri ta wurin zubar da jini da aka yi wa mutane.
Duk da haka, adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan sifili, kamar yadda jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin suka bayyana a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma, a kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a kasar Sin ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Yada HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce ga al'ummar LGBT a kasar Sin.
An yi watsi da jima'i a kasar Sin a shekara ta 1997, amma nuna bambanci ga 'yan luwadi na yau da kullum.
Idan aka yi la'akari da ƙa'idodin ƙasar, bincike ya nuna cewa tsakanin kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin 100 na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza za su auri mace.
Yawancin cututtuka na cuta suna faruwa ne domin rashin yin jima'i.
Tun shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samun damar yin amfani da maganin HIV a duniya a matsayin wani ɓangare na ƙoƙarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa wani ma'aikaci ya yi amfani da bayanan sanatocin jam'iyyar Republican kuma ta kawar da "ƙaryace-ƙaryace masu haɗari" da "kide-kide na ƙulla yarjejeniya"
A ranar Asabar, wakilin Amurka Maxine Waters ya yi zargin cewa wani ma'aikacinta ya wallafa bayanan sirri na wasu Sanatocin Jamhuriyar Amurka uku a shafukan Wikipedia na 'yan majalisa.
'Yar Democrat ta Los Angeles ta yi ikirarin cewa masu sukar da kuma shafukan yanar gizo na dama sun yi amfani da wannan bukatar.
Waters ya ce a wani sakon Twitter: "Karyata, ƙarya da kuma karin karya".
An ce bayanan da aka wallafa sun ƙunshi adiresoshin da lambobin waya na Sanatocin Amurka Lindsey Graham, na Carolina ta Kudu, da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, duka biyu daga Utah.
Wani mutum da ba a san shi ba a birnin Capitol ya wallafa wannan bayanin a ranar Alhamis a kan layi a lokacin da ake tattaunawa a kan takardar da ake yi wa dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh na Majalisar Dattawa game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i.
Bayan an gano cewa wasu sanatoci uku sun yi tambaya game da Kavanaugh, sai aka yi amfani da wannan bayanin.
Shafuka masu kiyayewa, kamar Gateway Pundit da RedState, sun ba da rahoton cewa adireshin IP ɗin da ke gano tushen wallafe-wallafen yana da alaƙa da ofishin Waters kuma yana bayyana bayanin wani memba na ma'aikatan Waters, Capitol ya zargi.
Waters ya ci gaba da cewa: "Wannan zargin da ba shi da tushe ba ƙarya ce gaba ɗaya kuma ƙarya ce kawai.
"Wani ma'aikaci na, wanda sun yi amfani da shi don gano ko kuma tabbatar da cewa an yi masa laifi saboda waɗannan ƙarar da aka yi masa, ba shi da alhakin wannan ɓoyewar.
Wannan ƙarar da ba ta da tushe ba ƙarya ce kuma zato ne kawai".
Sanarwar Waters ta haifar da sukar kan layi da sauri, gami da na tsohon sakataren yada labarai na Fadar White House, Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan ƙin yarda da shi yana cike da fushi", in ji Fleischer.
"Wannan ya sa ta yi tunanin cewa ba ta da halin da za ta kasance a majalisar.
Idan aka zargi wani da wani abu da bai yi ba, kada ka yi fushi.
Kada ka yi ƙoƙari ka yi abin da ba ka so.
Kada ka yi tambaya game da dalilin da ya sa ake tuhumar da kai.
Ya kamata ya kasance da kwanciyar hankali".
Fleischer ya bayyana cewa ya kwatanta yadda Waters ya yi da sukar 'yan Democrat na Judge Kavanaugh, wanda masu sukar suka zargi da yin fushi sosai a lokacin zaman ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican da ya fito don kawar da Waters a zaben rabin lokaci, ya kuma bayyana ra'ayinsa a shafin Twitter.
"Ko da yake gaskiya ne", ta wallafa a shafinta na Twitter.
A cikin jawabinsa, Waters ya ce ofishinsa ya sanar da hukumomi da jami'an tsaro masu dacewa game da waɗannan maganganun zamba.
"Za mu tabbatar da cewa an gano masu aikata laifin", in ji ta, "kuma za a ɗauke su da alhakin duk wani aiki da suka yi da ya cutar da kowane ɗayan ma'aikatan na".
Ƙididdigar Johnny English Strikes Again: Ƙididdigar ɗan leƙen asiri ta Rowan Atkinson
An riga an saba yin amfani da shi don neman nassoshin Brexit a kowane sabon fim da ke da tsarin Burtaniya, kuma wannan sake fasalin wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo na Johnny English, wanda aka haifa a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya sake bayyana a 2011 tare da Johnny English Reborn, ba banda.
Wannan ba'a da ba'a game da yadda muke da mutunci zai zama sabuwar dama ga fitar da ƙasar?
Ko ta yaya, baƙar fata mai ido da fuskar roba Johnny English ya sami damar sabunta lasisinsa na biyu don ya juya komai.
A bayyane yake, shi ne ɗan ɓoye na sirri wanda, duk da ƙarancin da'awarsa na sha'awar sha'awa, yana da ɗan Clouseau, wani tabo na Mr. Bean da kuma taɓa wannan mutumin wanda ke ba da sanarwa ɗaya ga batun Motocin wuta a bikin buɗe gasar Olympics ta London 2012.
A asali, an dogara ne akan matafiyi na duniya mai ban mamaki Atkinson wanda ke wakiltar tallan talabijin da aka manta da su yanzu daga Barclaycard, inda ya yi shuka rikici a ko'ina.
Akwai lokatai biyu masu kyau a wannan tafiya ta ƙarshe ta JE.
Yana son Johnny English wanda ke zuwa kusa da jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu wanda ke sanye da kayan kwalliya na zamani kuma ganyen hellice suna ƙunshe da kwalkwali.
Na ga baiwar Atkinson ga wasan kwaikwayo na zahiri, amma ban dariya yana da kyau kuma yana da ban mamaki, musamman saboda alamun fim "masu tsanani" kamar 007 da Mission Impossible yanzu sun haɗa da wasan kwaikwayo a matsayin kayan aiki.
Ba'a iya ganin cewa yara ne suka fi girma ba, kuma a ganina, abubuwan da Johnny English ya yi ba su da hankali kamar yadda yake nunawa a cikin Mr. Bean wanda Atkinson ya yi.
A yau, ana yawan cewa Birtaniya tana cikin matsala.
Wani dan fashin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin hanyar sadarwar leken asiri ta yanar gizo ta Burtaniya kuma ya bayyana ainihin dukkan jami'an Burtaniya a kan filin, wanda ya haifar da damuwa ga wakilin sabis, rawar da ke da matukar damuwa ga Kevin Eldon.
Wannan ita ce mafita ta ƙarshe ga firaministan da yake da girman kai da kuma mamakin mutum, wanda ya riga ya sha wahala daga cikakken rushewar rashin shahararren siyasa: Emma Thompson ta ba da mafi kyawun kanta tare da wannan mutumin Teresa-May, amma rubutun bai wuce ba.
Masu ba da shawara a harkokin leken asiri sun gaya masa cewa, yayin da kowane ɗan leken asiri mai aiki ya shiga cikin haɗari, dole ne ya dawo da wani daga cikin ritaya.
Wannan ya hada da Johnny English, wanda yanzu yake aiki a matsayin malamin wata makarantar ilimi, amma yana koyar da darussan ba bisa ka'ida ba game da yadda ake zama dan sanda mai ɓoyewa, tare da wasu kyawawan abubuwa, kamar lokacin da English ke ba da makarantar leken asiri wanda ke kama da makarantar rock.
An dawo da English da sauri zuwa Whitehall don haɗuwa ta gaggawa tare da mai shan wahala Bough, rawar da ya sake buga Ben Miller.
Yanzu Bough mutum ne mai aure, yana da alaƙa da kwamandan jirgin ruwa, wani rawar da ke da sha'awa, wanda Vicki Pepperdine ta ɗan rasa amfani da ita.
Don haka, Batman da Robin na lokacin da abubuwa suka zama mummunan aiki ga sirrin sarautarsa sun sake shiga aiki kuma sun sami Olga Kurylenko mai ban mamaki femme fatale Ophelia Bulletova.
A halin yanzu, Firayim Minista yana cikin haɗari a ƙarƙashin ƙirar mai tallata fasaha mai ƙwarewa wanda ke da'awar cewa zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Burtaniya: Jason Volta mai ban tsoro, wanda Jake Lacy ya wakilta.
English da Bough sun fara tafiyarsu ta hanyar hauka mai ban dariya: suna ado da kayan aiki, suna ƙona gidan abinci na Faransa mai sauri, suna shuka rikici ta hanyar yin fashi a kan jirgin ruwan alatu na Volta kuma English yana haifar da babban rikici yayin ƙoƙarin amfani da kwalkwali na gaskiya na kama-da-wane don sanin abubuwan da ke cikin gidan Volta.
Dukkanin abubuwan da aka nuna sun fito ne daga wannan jerin, amma duk da sauƙin da kuma sautin da ya gabatar, duk abin da ya haɗu yana kama da shirin yara.
Abubuwa na al'ada.
Kamar sauran fina-finai na Johnny English, ba shi da taimako a yi tunanin ko masana'antar fim ta ba Rowan Atkinson rawar da za ta yi adalci ga basirarsa.
Jam'iyyar Labour ta musanta cewa tana shirin samar da makonni hudu na aiki ga 'yan Birtaniya, kuma suna biyan su biyar.
Jam'iyyar Labour ta Jeremy Corbyn za ta yi la'akari da shirin da zai sa Britaniya ta yi aiki kwana hudu a mako kuma ta biya biyar.
A cewar wani rahoto, jam'iyyar ta so shugabannin kamfanoni su ba ma'aikata kuɗin da suka samu daga juyin juya halin fasaha ta wucin gadi ta ba su wata rana ta biki.
Ma'aikata za su yi amfani da ƙarshen mako na kwana uku, amma za su samu albashin da ya yi daidai.
Majiyoyin sun ce wannan ra'ayin ya dace da tsarin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyun da kuma shirin da ake yi na karkatar da kasar zuwa ga ma'aikata.
Canjin zuwa mako na aiki na kwana huɗu yana da goyon bayan ƙungiyar kwadago ta Trades Union Congress a matsayin hanyar da ma'aikata za su iya amfana daga canjin tattalin arziki.
Wani masaniyar jam'iyyar Labour ya bayyana a cikin The Sunday Times: "An sa ran za a sanar da sake duba siyasa kafin karshen shekara.
Ba za a yi aiki ba, amma mako na aiki na kwana huɗu yana da burin da ya dace da hangen nesa na jam'iyyar na daidaita tattalin arziki a madadin ma'aikaci da kuma tsarin masana'antu na jam'iyyar.
Jam'iyyar Labor ba za ta kasance ta farko ba da goyon baya ga wannan ra'ayin, tun da Jam'iyyar Green ta yi alkawarin mako na aiki na kwanaki hudu a lokacin yakin neman zaben 2017 na gaba.
Duk da haka, Jam'iyyar Labor ba ta tallafawa wannan burin a yau.
A cewar wani mai magana da yawun jam'iyyar Labor: "Mako na aiki na kwana hudu ba siyasa ba ce kuma jam'iyyar ba ta la'akari da hakan.
Ministan inuwa John McDonnell ya yi amfani da taron jam'iyyarsa na makon da ya gabata don bayyana hangen nesa game da juyin juya halin zamantakewa a tattalin arziki.
McDonnell ya nuna ƙudurinsa na sake dawo da ikon "masu gudanarwa marasa suna" da "masu fa'ida" a cikin kamfanonin sabis na gwamnati.
Shirin ministan a cikin inuwa kuma yana nuna cewa masu hannun jari na kamfanonin ruwa na iya rashin dawo da duk saka hannun jari, saboda gwamnatin Labor na iya amfani da "saki" don laifofin da ta gano.
Ta kuma tabbatar da shirye-shiryen sanya ma'aikata a cikin kwamitocin kamfanoni da ƙirƙirar kudaden mallakar mallakar mallakar don sadar da kashi 10% na hannun jari na kamfanonin kamfanoni masu zaman kansu ga ma'aikata, waɗanda ke fatan samun riba ta shekara-shekara har zuwa GBP 500.
Lindsey Graham, John Kennedy ya bayyana wa "60 Minutes" ko binciken FBI na Kavanaugh zai iya sa su canja ra'ayinsu.
Binciken FBI na zargin da aka yi wa Alkalin Brett Kavanaugh ya jinkirta zaben karshe na takararsa na kotun koli da ya kai mako guda, kuma ya haifar da tambaya game da ko binciken hukumar zai iya rinjayar wani Sanata na Republican ya janye goyon bayansa.
A wata hira da za a buga a ranar Lahadi, mai ba da rahoto ga "60 Minutes" Scott Pelley ya tambayi Sanatocin Republican John Kennedy da Lindsey Graham ko FBI za ta iya fitar da wani abu da zai sa su canja ra'ayinsu.
Kennedy ya nuna cewa ya fi abokinsa a South Carolina bude ido.
"Ina da gaske", in ji Kennedy.
"A lokacin da na yi magana da shi na ce na yi magana da Alkalin Kavanaugh.
Na kira shi lokacin da aka yi zargin, kuma na tambaye shi ko ya yi hakan.
Ya kasance mai ƙarfi, mai ƙuduri da kuma gaba gaɗi".
Amma muryar Graham ta yi kama da ta ƙone wuta.
"Ina da ra'ayina game da Brett Kavanaugh kuma zan gabatar da zargi mai fashewa", in ji ta.
"Dr. Ford, ban san abin da ya faru ba, amma na san wannan: Brett ya ƙaryata", in ji Graham, yana nufin Christine Blasey Ford.
"Ba wanda zai iya tabbatar da hakan.
Yana da shekara 36.
Ba zan iya ganin wani abu ya canja ba".
Shin, shin, akwai wani abu da aka yi don rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar, birnin New York zai karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen, wani taron kiɗa na shekara-shekara, wanda ke nuna shirin taurari masu ban sha'awa, waɗanda ke da manufa mai ban sha'awa: kawar da talauci a duniya.
A karo na bakwai na wannan shekara, bikin na Global Citizen zai ga dubban mutane sun taru a yankin Great Lawn na Central Park ba wai kawai don jin daɗin wasan kwaikwayon kamar na Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, har ma don wayar da kan jama'a game da burin duniya na kawar da talauci a duniya kafin 2030.
Bikin Global Citizen, wanda aka fara a 2012, wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya ta kasa da kasa da ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke taimakawa wajen yaki da ta.
Don samun shiga kyauta don taron (sai dai idan wani ya so ya biya VIP), masu halarta suna buƙatar yin jerin ayyuka ko "aiki", kamar su yin aikin sa kai, aika imel zuwa ga shugaban duniya, yin kiran waya ko kowane aiki don tada hankalin game da burin kawar da talauci.
Mene ne ya faru da Global Citizen a yanzu da yake da shekaru 12 kafin ya kai ga burinsa?
Tunanin ba da kyauta ga mutane tare da wani kyauta ne mai kyau hanyar rinjayar su da bukatar kira zuwa ga aiki ko kawai wani karin yanayin da muke kira "clictivism" (mutumin da ya yi tunanin cewa ya sa bambanci ta hanyar sanya hannu a kan wani online request ko aika da wani tweet?
Tun daga shekara ta 2011, Global Citizen ta ce ta yi rajistar fiye da miliyan 19 na "aikin" daga masu goyon bayanta, wanda ya taimaka wajen cimma manufofi da yawa.
Ya ce wadannan ayyukan sun taimaka wajen sa shugabannin duniya su sanar da alkawuran da manufofi masu kama da dala biliyan 37, wanda zai shafi rayuwar mutane sama da miliyan 2.250 kafin 2030.
A farkon 2018, ƙungiyar ta ambata alkawura 390 da sanarwa daga hannun jari, wanda aka riga an biya ko an karɓi aƙalla dala biliyan 10.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa, a yanzu, kudaden da aka tanadar sun shafi kusan mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Wasu daga cikin manyan alkawuran sun hada da The Power of Nutrition Foundation, wata kungiya ta masu zuba jari da masu samar da kayayyaki da ke Burtaniya, wadda ta yi alkawarin "taimaka yara su girma kamar yadda ya kamata" kuma ta yi alkawarin aikawa da dala miliyan 35 zuwa Rwanda don taimakawa wajen yaki da rashin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar bayan ta karbi fiye da 4,700 daga Global Citizens.
