Wakilan jihohi 18 da kuma gundumar sun gabatar da wani amicus curiae a ranar Juma'a a Washington don tallafawa mai neman mafaka da ke kalubalantar siyasa, a cewar NBC News.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan karar Grace v. Sessions da Kungiyar 'Yancin Bil Adama ta Amurka ta gabatar a watan Agusta a kan manufofin tarayya ba.
