Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, yana kaddamar da wani sabon kamfani wanda ke neman yin gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Aikin ƙarshe na almara na fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne wanda ya dogara da dandamali na buɗe lambar Solid na Berners-Lee.
Ƙungiyoyin Solid suna ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma waɗanda za su iya samun dama ga wasu bayanai.
A wata hira ta musamman da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi dariya cewa manufar ɓoyayyen Inrupt ita ce "mulki a duniya".
"Dole ne mu yi yanzu", in ji shi daga kamfanin.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar dandamali na Solid don bawa masu amfani damar ƙirƙirar nasu "gidan ajiyar bayanan kan layi" ko POD.
Yana iya ƙunsar jerin sunayen lambobin sadarwa, jerin ayyukan da ba a yi ba, kalandar, ɗakin karatu na kiɗa da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack, da Spotify. Duk suna samuwa a cikin mai bincike a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke keɓewa ga ajiyar bayanan sirri na kan layi shi ne cewa mai amfani ne ke yanke shawarar wanda zai iya samun dama ga wasu bayanai.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "karfafawa ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar babban mai ba da shawara na kamfanin, John Bruce, ita ce kamfanin ya haɗa albarkatu, matakai da ƙwarewa masu dacewa don dandamali na Solid ya kasance ga kowa.
A halin yanzu, Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu haɓaka samfuri da aka ɗauka don aiki a kan aikin da kuma ƙungiyar masu ba da kyauta na masu ba da kyauta.
Daga wannan makon, masu haɓaka fasaha a duk faɗin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen su na rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin gidan yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce babu wani a cikin tawagarsa da ke magana da "Facebook da Google game da ko ya kamata a kawo canji mai zurfi inda dukkanin tsarin kasuwanci ke zama cikakke a cikin dare.
"Ba mu nemi izinin su ba".
A wata sanarwa a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa manufa ta Inrupt ita ce samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu don taimakawa kare mutuncin da ingancin sabon shafin yanar gizon da aka haɗa a cikin dandamali na Solid".
A 1994, Berners-Lee ya canza Intanet lokacin da ya kafa World Wide Web Consortium a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Har ma a lokacin ƙaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da kasancewa wanda ya kafa kuma ya jagoranci World Wide Web Consortium, World Wide Web Foundation da Open Data Institute.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da wannan sabon zamanin yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
