Firist na Ikilisiyar Ingila kawai wanda ya sami Gicciye na Nasara a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na ɗaya a matsayin mai yaƙi an girmama shi a garinsu shekaru 100 bayan haka.
Lt. Col. da kuma mai daraja Bernard Vann ya sami lambar yabo a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918 don hari a Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Duk da haka, an kashe shi ta hanyar mai fasa kwanaki hudu daga baya kuma bai san cewa ya sami babbar darajar soja ta Burtaniya ba.
'Ya'yanta biyu sun buɗe wani dutsen tunawa a wani gangamin Asabar a Rushden, Northamptonshire.
Ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, Michael Vann, ya ce "mai ban mamaki ne" cewa an gabatar da dutsen a daidai shekaru 100 bayan nasarar da kakansa ya yi.
A cewar The London Gazette, a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Lieutenant Colonel Vann ya jagoranci rundunarsa ta hanyar Canal de Saint-Quentin "ta hanyar hazo mai zurfi da kuma karkashin wuta mai tsanani na bindigogi da na'urori masu linzami".
Daga baya ya gudu zuwa layin wuta kuma, tare da "mafi girman ƙarfin hali" ya sa layin ya ci gaba kafin ya jefa kansa a kan gun tare da hannu ɗaya kuma ya bar mambobin ƙungiyar uku sun firgita.
Wani dan wasan Jamus ya kashe Lt. Col. a ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918, wata daya kafin yakin ya ƙare.
Michael Vann (72) ya ce ayyukan kakansa wani abu ne da ba za a iya daidaita shi ba, wanda ke sa ka ji cewa kana da tawali'u.
Shi da ɗan'uwansa, Dr. James Vann, sun kuma bar kambi bayan gangamin, wanda Brentwood Imperial Youth Band ya jagoranci.
Michael Vann ya ce yana jin daɗin kasancewa cikin bikin kuma ya kara da cewa ƙarfin jarumi na gaske yana nunawa ta hanyar goyon bayan da zai samu daga mutane da yawa.
Masu sha'awar LTMMA da suka yi bacci duk dare don kallon Bellator 206, sun ga Peppa Pig a maimakon haka
Ka yi tunanin kana farkawa duk dare don ka kalli Bellator 206 kuma an hana ka ganin babban taron.
San Jose's poster ya ƙunshi gwagwarmaya 13, ciki har da shida daga cikin babban katin kuma ana iya kallon su a kai a kai duk dare a Burtaniya akan Channel 5.
A karfe 6:00, yayin da Gegard Mousasi da Rory MacDonald ke shirin yin gwagwarmaya, masu kallo a Burtaniya sun yi mamakin lokacin da aka canza shirye-shiryen zuwa Peppa Pig.
Wasu sun yi fushi domin sun yi barci har zuwa safiya don su ga yaƙin.
Wani mai bi a shafin Twitter ya bayyana sauyin zuwa zane-zane a matsayin "wani irin rashin jin daɗi".
"Ka'idojin gwamnati sun ce a karfe 6:00 wannan abun ba daidai ba ne, don haka suka canza zuwa shirye-shiryen yara", in ji Dave Schwartz, mataimakin shugaban kasuwanci da sadarwa na Bellator, lokacin da aka tambaye shi game da sake watsa shirye-shirye.
"Ka sha da alade, a'a".
Shugaban kamfanin Bellator, Scott Coker, ya ce za su yi aiki a shirye-shiryen don haɗa masu kallo na Burtaniya a nan gaba.
"Ina tsammanin idan na yi tunani game da maimaitawa, ina tsammanin zai iya aiki", in ji Coker.
"Amma akwai karfe shida na safe na ranar Lahadi kuma ba za mu iya warware matsalar ba har sai ranar Lahadi a lokacinmu, Litinin a lokacinku.
Amma muna aiki a kai.
Ku yi imani da ni, lokacin da na sauya tashar, akwai saƙonni da yawa da suke zuwa da kuma zuwa, kuma ba duka suna da kyau ba.
Mun yi kokarin warware matsalar, muna ganin matsalar fasaha ce.
Amma ba haka ba ne. Wata matsala ce ta gwamnati.
Na yi alkawari ba za ta sake faruwa ba.
Mun yi ƙoƙari mu sake nuna wa magoya baya, amma ba mu yi nasara ba.
Wannan yanayi ne mai ban tausayi".
Desert Island Disc: Tom Daley ya ji kasa game da jima'i
Dan wasan tsalle-tsalle na Olympic Tom Daley ya ce ya girma yana jin ya fi sauran mutane saboda jima'i, amma wannan ya ba shi dalili don cin nasara.
Dan wasan mai shekara 24 ya ce bai fahimci cewa kowa ba ne kamarsa ba sai da ya shiga makarantar sakandare.
A shirin Desert Island Discs na Radio 4, wanda Lauren Laverne ya gabatar, ya ce yana magana ne game da haƙƙin gay don ba da bege ga wasu mutane.
Ya kuma ce kasancewa uba ya sa ya daina damuwa game da lashe gasar Olympics.
Kirsty Young, mai gabatar da shirin na dogon lokaci, ta yi watanni da yawa ba ta aiki saboda rashin lafiya.
Daley, wanda ya bayyana a matsayin wanda ya halaka jirgin ruwa a shirin farko na Laverne, ya ce ya ji "ƙananan" fiye da sauran saboda "ba shi da karɓa a zamantakewar jama'a kamar yara mata da yara".
Ya ce: "Yau, waɗannan jin ƙanƙan da bambanci sun kasance abubuwan da suka ba ni iko da ƙarfi don yin nasara".
Ta ce tana son ta tabbatar da cewa ita "wani abu ne", don kada ta sa kowa baƙin ciki sa'ad da ta gano jima'i.
Dan wasan da ya lashe lambar tagulla na Olympics sau biyu ya zama babban mai tallata LGBT kuma ya yi amfani da hotonsa a wasannin Commonwealth na bara a Ostiraliya don neman ƙarin ƙasashe su ƙyale cin zarafin luwadi.
Ya ce ya yi magana ne domin yana jin yana da sa'a don ya iya rayuwa a fili ba tare da wani tasiri ba kuma yana so ya ba da bege ga wasu mutane.
Mai cin gashin duniya ya bayyana cewa ya yi ƙaunar wani mutum, mai shirya fim din Amurka, Dustin Lance Black, wanda ya sadu a 2013, "ya mamaye ni".
A shekarar da ta gabata, Daley ya auri Oscar mai shekaru 20, amma ya ce bambancin shekaru bai taba zama matsala ba.
A cewarsa, idan ka sha wahala a lokacin da kake matashi (ya halarci wasannin Olympics na farko a lokacin da yake da shekaru 14 kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon daji shekaru uku bayan haka), yana da wuya a sami wani ɗan shekara ɗaya da ya taɓa fuskantar irin wannan tashin hankali da rashin ƙarfi.
Ma'aurata sun haifi jariri a watan Yuni wanda suka sanya masa suna Robert Ray Black-Daley.
"Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, duk abin da nake bukata shi ne in lashe zinariya a gasar Olympics", in ji ta.
"Akwai abubuwa da suka fi na zinariya na Olympics muhimmanci.
Gwarzon zinare na na Olympics shi ne Robbie".
Ɗansa yana da suna ɗaya da mahaifinsa, Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011, yana da shekaru 40 daga ciwon daji na kwakwalwa.
Daley ya ce mahaifinsa bai yarda da cewa ya mutu ba kuma daya daga cikin abubuwan da ya tambaya shi ne ko sun riga sun sami tikiti zuwa London 2012, saboda yana son kasancewa a cikin layi na farko.
"Ba zan iya ce masa 'Baba, ba za ka kasance a can domin ya dauki na farko jere", ya ce.
"A lokacin da na kama hannunsa, ya daina numfashi kuma ba sai da ya mutu ba, na yarda cewa ba zan iya cin nasara ba", in ji ta.
A shekara ta gaba, Daley ya yi gasar Olympics ta 2012 kuma ya lashe tagulla.
"Na san cewa wannan shi ne burina na dukan rayuwata: tsalle a gaban taron a gida a wasu wasannin Olympics. Babu wani abin da ya fi wannan jin dadi", ta ce.
Ya kuma yi wahayi zuwa ga zabar waƙar ta farko (Proud na Heather Small), wanda ya ji yayin shirye-shiryen wasannin Olympics kuma har yanzu yana sanya shi fata na kaza.
Desert Island Discs ya fito ne a tashar BBC Radio 4 a ranar Lahadi da karfe 11:15 na dare.
Wani Mickelson mai lalata ya bayyana a gasar Ryder Cup a ranar Asabar
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai buga rikodin ranar Lahadi a wasansa na 47 na gasar Ryder Cup, amma dole ne ya canza yanayin jikinsa idan ba ya son ya zama mai takaici.
Mickelson, wanda zai shiga taron na shekara biyu don karya rikodin sau 12, ya gabatar da kyaftin Jim Furyk don hanyoyin fourballs da foursomes na Asabar.
Maimakon kasancewa a tsakiyar aikin, kamar yadda Amurka ta saba yi, wanda ya lashe manyan gasa biyar ya raba lokacinsa tsakanin yin wasan motsa jiki da aiki a wasan su a filin wasa, tare da fatan gyara abin da ya cutar da shi.
Bai taɓa yin direbobi masu kai tsaye ba, ko da a lokacin da ya fi tsayi a cikin aikinsa, amma ɗan wasan mai shekaru 48 ba shine mafi kyawun zaɓi ba don ƙalubalen Le Golf National, inda dogon rough ke amfani da shi don azabtar da bugun da aka ɓata.
Kuma idan tarihinsa bai isa ya sa ya yi baƙin ciki ba, Mickelson, a wasan tara na ranar Lahadi, zai fuskanci gwarzon gasar cin kofin Birtaniya, Francesco Molinari, wanda ya shiga tare da rookie Tommy Fleetwood don lashe wasanni huɗu na wannan makon.
Idan 'yan wasan Amirka, da maki hudu a farkon wasannin guda 12, suka fara da ƙarfi, wasan Mickelson zai iya zama mai mahimmanci.
Furyk ya nuna cewa ya amince da wannan mutumin, ba tare da ya ƙara faɗi kome ba.
Furyk ya ce: "Ya fahimci matsayinsa sosai a wannan rana, ya yi mini wani bugun baya kuma ya kewaye ni da hannu yayin da yake gaya mini cewa zai kasance a shirye a gobe".
"Yana da babban amincewa da kansa.
Wannan gidan wasan kwaikwayo ne kuma ya ba da gudummawa sosai ga waɗannan ƙungiyoyin a baya da kuma wannan makon.
Wataƙila ban yi tunanin zai buga wasanni biyu ba.
Na yi tunanin hakan, amma wannan shi ne yadda nake horarwa kuma wannan shi ne yadda muke ganin ya kamata mu ci gaba.
Yana son kasancewa a wurin, kamar kowa".
A ranar Lahadi, Mickelson zai ci rikodin Nick Faldo na mafi yawan wasannin Ryder Cup da aka buga.
Yana iya nufin ƙarshen tseren Ryder Cup wanda bai daidaita rikodin mutum ba.
Mickelson ya samu nasara 18, 20 da kuma 7 a raga, duk da cewa Furyk ya bayyana cewa kasancewarsa ta kawo rashin amfani ga tawagar.
"Yana da ban dariya, mai ba'a, mai ban dariya, yana son yin wa mutane ba'a kuma yana da kyau a cikin tawagar", in ji shi.
Ina ganin matasa 'yan wasan sun ji daɗin kasancewa tare da shi a wannan makon, abin da ya yi farin ciki sosai.
Yana kawo abubuwa da yawa a waje da wasan.
Shugaban Turai Thomas Bjorn ya san cewa za a iya kawar da wannan fa'idar nan da nan
Thomas Bjorn, shugaban Turai, ya san cewa farawa da babbar fa'ida a wasan guda ɗaya na Ryder Cup na ƙarshe na iya zama rana mai wuya.
Danish ya fara a shekara ta 1997 a Valderrama, lokacin da ƙungiyar da Seve Ballesteros ke jagoranta ta sami fifiko na maki biyar akan ƙungiyar Amurka, amma a ƙarshe sun sami nasara ta ƙarami, 14,5-13,5.
Ka ci gaba da tuna cewa muna da babban fa'ida a Valderrama; muna da babban fa'ida a Brookline, inda muka rasa, da kuma a Valderrama, inda muka ci nasara, amma ba da daɗewa ba, Bjorn ya bayyana, a cikin hoto, bayan ganin nasarar ƙungiyar 2018 ta 5-3 a ranar Jumma'a da jiya, wanda ya bar alamar a 10-6 a Le Golf National.
Tarihin ya koya mana ni da sauran 'yan wasan cewa ba a gama ba tukuna.
Dole ne ku tafi duk motar gobe.
Dole ne ka fita ka yi shi da kyau.
Wannan ba ya ƙare har sai maki sun kai alamar.
Muna da manufa, mu yi ƙoƙari mu lashe kyautar, kuma dole ne mu ci gaba da mayar da hankali don yin hakan.
Na riga na fada muku, na mayar da hankali ne ga 'yan wasan 12 da muke da su a tawagar, amma kuma ina da masu fafatawa a gabanmu: 'yan wasan duniya mafi kyau.
Bjorn ya yi farin ciki da yadda 'yan wasansa suka yi a filin golf mai wuya, kuma ya kara da cewa: "Ba zan yi sauri ba.
Zai zama daban gobe.
Nan gaba, sakamakon mutum zai kawo canji a dukan duniya.
Yana da kyau ka kasance tare da abokin aiki a lokacin da kome ya tafi daidai, amma wasan kwaikwayo na mutum yana gwada ƙwarewarka a wasan golf.
Wannan shi ne saƙon da za ka yi wa 'yan wasanka, ka yi amfani da abin da kake da shi don yin nasara a gobe.
A wannan lokacin, ka bar abokin aikinka kuma ya fita ya kuma fitar da mafi kyau daga kansa.
A akasin Bjorn, shugaban mai fafatawa, Jim Furyk, yana fatan 'yan wasan suyi aiki mafi kyau a matsayin mutum fiye da na ƙungiya, ban da Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka tara maki uku daga hudu.
Furyk ya san fuskokin biyu na tsabar kudi a kan tashin hankali na ranar ƙarshe, tun da yake ya kasance wani ɓangare na ƙungiyar da ta ci nasara a Brookline kafin ya ƙare rasa a cikin Mu'ujizar Medinah wanda ya ci Turai.
"Na tuna da dukan kalmomin", ya amsa tambayar game da yadda Ben Crenshaw, kyaftin din 1999, ya motsa 'yan wasansa kafin ranar ƙarshe.
"Yau muna da manyan wasanni 12, amma muna so mu fara da kyau, kamar yadda muka gani a Brookline da Medinah.
Idan akwai wani rukuni da ke da kwarin gwiwa, za a yi matsin lamba a kan waɗannan manyan wasan.
Mun shirya tsarin da ya dace da yanayin da kuma yadda za mu yi sihiri gobe.
Thomas yana da kalubalen ƙoƙarin fara fara gwagwarmayar da Rory McIlroy a wasan farko, tare da Paul Casey, Justin Rose, Jon Rahm, Tommy Fleetwood da Ian Poulter a matsayin sauran Turawa a farkon rabin tsari.
"Na zabi wannan tsari ne domin ina ganin ya shafi dukan yiwuwar", in ji Bjorn game da zaɓinsa don gwagwarmayar mutum.
Sabuwar jirgin saman Jamus, da aka sake turawa
Sabuwar jirgin ruwan jirgin saman na Jamus ya kamata a kammala shi a cikin 2014 don maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwa na lokacin Cold War, amma ba zai yi ba, aƙalla, har zuwa shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin inganci da ƙaruwa a farashin, a cewar kafofin watsa labarai na gida.
Kammalawar jirgin ruwa na Rheinland-Pfalz, babban jirgin ruwa na sabon jirgin ruwa na Baden-Württemberg, an jinkirta har zuwa rabin farkon 2019, a cewar jaridar Die Zeit, wanda ya ambaci wani mai magana da yawun soja.
Ya kamata jirgin ya shiga cikin Navy a shekara ta 2014, amma matsalolin da suka biyo baya sun nuna ƙarshen wannan aikin mai ban sha'awa.
Jirgin ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Württemberg da Rundunar Sojan Ruwa ta ba da umarni a shekara ta 2007 za su maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
An yi imanin cewa zai haɗa da makami mai ƙarfi, wani rukunin makamai masu linzami da makamai masu linzami, da fasaha kan ayyukan ɓoyewa, kamar radar mai raguwa, infrared da sa hannu na sauti.
Sauran abubuwan da suka fi dacewa sun haɗa da tsawon lokaci tsakanin kiyayewa: Ya kamata a iya amfani da sabbin jiragen ruwa har zuwa shekaru biyu ba tare da wucewa ta tashar jiragen ruwa na ƙasa ba.
Duk da haka, waɗannan jinkiri na ci gaba suna nufin cewa jiragen ruwa na gaba, wanda aka yi hasashen za su iya tsarawa a Jamus a matsayin iko mai ƙarfi a ƙasashen waje, za su riga sun tsufa lokacin da suka fara aiki, a cewar Die Zeit.
Famagata F125 da ta yi rashin alheri ta zama labari a shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da Rundunar Sojan Jamus ta ƙi jirgin kuma ta mayar da shi zuwa Blohm & Voss na Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar sojin ta ba da jirgin ruwa ga mai ginin da aka kawo.
Ba a san cikakken bayani game da dalilan da ya sa ya dawo ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ambaci wasu "kasusuwa da fasaha" na jirgin da suka sa ya zama mara amfani idan aka yi amfani da shi a ayyukan yaƙi.
Matsalolin fasaha suna da mahimmanci, tun da kimanin ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa 120, rabin ma'aikatan da ake buƙata don tsoffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen, suna aiki a kan jiragen ruwa na Baden-Württemberg.
Bugu da ƙari, an kuma san nauyin jirgin ya wuce kima, wanda ke rage yawan aikinsa kuma yana iyakance ikon Navy don ƙara ƙarin haɓakawa a nan gaba.
An yi imanin cewa jirgin Rheinland-Pfalz, na tan 7,000, zai yi nauyi sau biyu fiye da jiragen ruwa na irin wannan aji da Jamus suka yi amfani da su a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Baya ga kayan da ba su da kyau, farashin aikin, wanda ya haɗa da horar da ma'aikatan, kuma yana fara haifar da matsala.
An yi imanin cewa an samu kudi mai yawa na Euro biliyan 3.1 daga kasafin kudin da aka fara da na Euro biliyan 2.2.
Matsalolin sabbin jiragen ruwa sun zama batun mahimmanci, idan aka yi la'akari da sanarwar kwanan nan da ke nuna cewa ƙarfin sojojin ruwa na Jamus yana raunana.
A wannan shekara, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin kare kariya na majalisar dokokin Jamus, ya yarda cewa Rundunar Sojan Ruwa ta rasa jiragen ruwa da za su iya amfani da su.
Jami'in ya ce halin ya kara muni a tsawon lokaci saboda an daina amfani da tsoffin jiragen ruwa, amma ba a sake samar da su ba.
Ya yi nadama cewa babu wani jirgin ruwa na Baden-Württemberg da zai iya shiga cikin rundunar sojan.
Gidauniyar Ƙasa ta yi leƙen asiri a kan rayuwar ratpenats
Wani sabon bincike da aka yi a wani gonar da ke cikin Highlands na Scotland ya nuna yadda 'yan daji suke amfani da shimfidar wuri don su ci abinci.
Ana sa ran binciken zai iya kawo sabon bayani game da halayyar waɗannan tsuntsaye masu tashi da kuma taimakawa a ayyukan kiyayewa na gaba.
Masana kimiyya na National Foundation of Scotland za su ci gaba da nazarin soprano da kuma kullun, ban da arewacin kunnuwa da ruwa a cikin Inverewe Botanical Garden, wanda ke cikin Wester Ross.
Za a sanya masu yin rikodin musamman a wurare masu mahimmanci na dukiya don bin diddigin ayyukan ratpenats a lokacin bazara.
Masu aikin sa kai da kuma ma'aikatan Hukumar Kiwon Lafiya ta Burtaniya za su yi bincike ta hannu da na'urori masu ganowa.
Binciken sauti na rikodin da masana suka yi zai ƙayyade yadda ake sautin ratpenats da kuma abin da kowane jinsin yake yi.
Da wannan bayanin, za a ƙirƙiri rahoto da taswirar yanayi don ƙirƙirar cikakken hoto a kan sikelin yanayin halayensu.
Rob Dewar, mai ba da shawara kan kiyaye yanayi na Ƙungiyar Ƙasar Scotland, yana fatan sakamakon zai nuna waɗanne wurare ne suka fi muhimmanci ga ratpenets da kuma yadda kowane nau'i yake amfani da su.
Wannan bayanin zai taimaka wajen gano fa'idodi na ayyukan kula da mazauni, kamar samar da ciyawa, da kuma yadda za a inganta kula da gandun daji ga ratsan daji da sauran nau'ikan da suka danganci.
Yawan 'yan fashi a Scotland da kuma sauran ƙasashen Ingila ya ragu sosai a ƙarni na ƙarshe.
Ayyukan gina gine-gine da kuma gyara gine-gine suna barazana ga ratpenats, saboda suna shafar gidaje kuma suna iya haifar da asarar mazauna.
Turbin iska da hasken wuta suna da haɗari, kamar takarda mai ƙwayoyin cuta da kuma maganin sinadarai da ake amfani da su a kayan gini, da kuma hare-haren gidajen gida.
A gaskiya, ƙwari ba makafi ba ne.
Amma, saboda yawan farautar dare, kunnuwansu sun fi amfani da su fiye da idanunsu sa'ad da suke kama ganima.
Suna amfani da fasaha mai kyau na gano wuri ta hanyar eco don gano kwari da shinge da ke shiga cikin jirgin su.
