Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da tsunami da ya afkawa birnin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, a cewar hukumomi.
Saboda an katse hanyoyin sadarwa, ƙungiyoyin taimako ba su iya samun bayanai daga yankin Donggala ba, wani yanki a arewacin Palu mafi kusa da tsakiyar girgizar ƙasa mai girma 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, tsibirin Cèlebes:
Palu babban birnin lardin Cèlebes na Tsakiya ne, wanda ke kusa da bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Cèlebes, tare da kimanin mutane 379,800 a shekara ta 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka faru.
Donggala wani yanki ne wanda ke shimfidawa a tsawon kilomita 300 na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Cèlebes.
Regencia, yanki ne na gudanarwa wanda ba shi da lardin, yana da yawan mutane 299,200 a shekara ta 2017.
Fishing da noma sune ginshiƙan tattalin arzikin lardin Cèlebes ta Tsakiya, musamman a yankin bakin teku na Donggala.
Harkokin hakar nickel ma suna da mahimmanci a lardin, amma suna da mahimmanci, musamman, a Morowali, a bakin tekun ƙarshen Cèlebes.
A cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, Palu da Donggala sun sha wahala daga tsunami da yawa, a cewar hukumar hana bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a birnin Donggala.
A shekara ta 1996 kuma, tsunami ya faru a yammacin Donggala wanda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin Pacific na wuta kuma yawanci girgizar ƙasa tana faruwa a wurin.
Ga jerin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a gabar yamma ta lardin Aceh na Indonesiya, arewacin Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ya shafi gabar yamma ta Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Dubban mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudu da tsibirin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, kuma ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya lalata gabar kudu kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.6 ta girgiza wani yanki a garin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.5 ta girgiza tsibirin Mentawai, a gabar Sumatra, kuma ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Girgizar ƙasa mai sauƙi ta shafi mulkin Pidie Jaya a Aceh kuma ta haifar da lalacewa da firgici, yayin da mazauna suka tuna da mummunan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 2004.
A wannan lokacin, babu tsunami, amma sama da mutane 100 ne suka mutu a sakamakon rushewar gine-gine.
2018: An yi jerin manyan girgizar ƙasa a tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia wanda ya kashe mutane 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta rushe dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a cikin tarko na ɗan lokaci.
