Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun nemi hukuncin kisa na musamman ga wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a New York
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya na New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci na New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas: hukuncin kisa ne na musamman wanda ba a yi amfani da shi a jihar ba don aikata laifi na tarayya tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekaru 30, ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan titin keke na West Side Highway, a Lower Manhattan kuma ya gurgunta masu tafiya da kuma masu hawa keke a lokacin tafiyarsa, a watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe wadanda aka kashe takwas "da gangan" kuma "da gangan" ya haifar da mummunan rauni na mutum, a cewar sanarwar niyyar neman hukuncin kisa da aka gabatar a Kudancin Gundumar New York.
Dukkanin laifuffukan sun nuna cewa za a kashe su.
Makonni bayan harin, babban juriyar tarayya ta kai hari ga Saipov tare da takardar da aka shigar da shi da ta gaza 22 wanda ya haɗa da tuhuma takwas na kisan kai don amfanin aikata laifuka, wanda masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da su a cikin shari'o'in mafia, ban da aikata laifi na tashin hankali da lalata motocin mota.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci "shirye-shirye da tunani mai yawa" kuma sun bayyana yadda Saipov ya yi aiki a matsayin "mara mutuntaka, mai zalunci da lalata".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da raunuka, raunin da asarar ga dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", a cewar sanarwar niyya.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekara goma ta shige tun lokacin da kotun kudancin New York ta kai karar kisa.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa a kan kisan 'yan kasuwa biyu, amma a ƙarshe an yanke masa hukuncin rai a kurkuku a watan Satumba na 2009.
Lokaci na ƙarshe da aka yanke hukuncin kisa a cikin wani shari'ar tarayya a New York shine 1953 ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa don yin ayyukan leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
Dukansu Rosenbergs sun mutu a cikin kujerar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
