Jagoran 'yancin majalisar Nancy Pelosi ta ce dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh "tarihi ne" kuma halayensa ya hana shi aiki a Kotun Koli.
Pelosi ta yi wannan bayanin a wata hira a ranar Asabar a bikin Texas Tribune wanda ake yi a Austin, Texas.
"Ba zan iya barin tunanin cewa idan wata mace ta yi aiki a wannan hanyar ba, za a ce ta kasance 'mai tsananin rikici,' in ji Pelosi dangane da yadda ta amsa shaidar Kavanaugh a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa a ranar Alhamis.
Kavanaugh, a cikin tashin hankali, ya musanta zargin da ya yi wa Dr. Christine Blasey Ford na lalata lokacin da suke matasa.
A lokacin da ya fara jawabinsa, Kavanaugh ya nuna damuwa sosai, wani lokacin yana ihu kuma yana rashin kalmomi yayin da yake magana game da iyalinsa da shekarun da ya yi a makarantar sakandare.
Ya kuma yi Allah wadai da 'yan majalisar 'yan Democrat a fili, ya ce zargin da ake masa game da "matsayin mutum mai tsanani da kuma daidaitaccen kisa" da 'yan liberals suka shirya saboda Hillary Clinton ta rasa zaben shugaban kasa na 2016.
Pelosi ta ce shaidar Kavanaugh ta nuna cewa ba za ta iya aiki a Kotun Koli ba, saboda ta nuna rashin amincewar ta ga 'yan Democrat.
"Ina ganin ya yi wa kansa rashin cancanta da irin wannan magana da kuma yadda ya kai hari ga Clinton da 'yan Democrat", in ji shi.
Pelosi ya nuna jinkirin lokacin da aka tambaye shi ko zai yi ƙoƙarin ƙalubalanci zaben Kavanaugh, idan an tabbatar da shi, kuma idan 'yan Democrat suka sami rinjaye a majalisar wakilai.
"Wannan shi ne abin da zan iya cewa: idan ba ta gaya wa majalisa ko FBI gaskiya ba, ba wai kawai ba ta da ikon zama a Kotun Koli, amma ba a kotun da take yanzu ba", in ji Pelosi.
A halin yanzu, Kavanaugh yana aiki a matsayin mai shari'a a Kotun Kararraki don Circuit na District of Columbia.
Pelosi ta kara da cewa, a matsayinta na dimokradiyya, tana damuwa game da yanke shawara da Kavanaugh zai iya yankewa game da Dokar Kula da Kula da Lafiya ko kuma batun Roe da Wade, saboda tana ganin ita alƙali mai ra'ayin mazan jiya.
